snippet.title: Battery Jam - Nintendo Switch Trailer (North America)
snippet.description:
Use the Boombox to smash your opponents, capture their tiles and dominate the arena! Take on your friends in Battery Jam, a local multiplayer game of competitive territorial mayhem! 

Coming November 22 to North America!

https://www.batteryjam.com/
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/battery-jam-switch
